From 87b314d42c3a0370cd3c6bf7cef711b977582920 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Maxime Ripard <mripard@kernel.org>
Date: Thu, 13 Feb 2025 15:43:23 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 0268/1107] drm/bridge: Pass full state to atomic_disable

It's pretty inconvenient to access the full atomic state from
drm_bridges, so let's change the atomic_disable hook prototype to pass
it directly.

